INSTALLATION
    Just perform the usual incantation:

    gunzip Class-Inner-0.1.tar.gz
    tar -xvf Class-Inner-0.1.tar 
    cd Class-Inner-0.1
    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

